sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over User,OAuth: Flow 1: User Login and Dashboard Access

    User->>OAuth: 1. Login Request<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>OpenShift Credentials
    OAuth-->>User: 2. OAuth Token (Cookie)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    User->>Route: 3. GET /<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>OAuth Token
    Route->>Proxy: 4. Forward (reencrypt)<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS 1.2+
    Proxy->>Backend: 5. HTTP/8080<br/>X-Auth-Request-User/Groups Headers
    Backend->>K8sAPI: 6. Get User Resources<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: User Projects, CRs
    Backend-->>Proxy: 7. HTML Response<br/>HTTP/8080
    Proxy-->>Route: HTTPS/8443
    Route-->>User: HTTPS/443<br/>Dashboard UI

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Create Jupyter Notebook

    User->>Route: 1. POST /api/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>OAuth Bearer Token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward<br/>HTTPS/8443
    Proxy->>Backend: 2. POST /api/notebooks<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>User/Group Headers
    Backend->>K8sAPI: 3. Create Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: 4. Create PVC, ConfigMap, Secret<br/>HTTPS/6443
    Backend->>K8sAPI: 5. Create RoleBinding<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: CR Created
    Backend-->>Proxy: 6. Success Response<br/>HTTP/8080
    Proxy-->>Route: HTTPS/8443
    Route-->>User: HTTPS/443<br/>Notebook Created

    Note over User,Thanos: Flow 3: Query Prometheus Metrics

    User->>Route: 1. GET /api/prometheus/*<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>OAuth Bearer Token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward<br/>HTTPS/8443
    Proxy->>Backend: 2. GET /api/prometheus/*<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>User/Group Headers
    Backend->>Thanos: 3. PromQL Query<br/>HTTPS/9092 TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Thanos-->>Backend: 4. Metrics Data<br/>HTTPS/9092
    Backend-->>Proxy: 5. JSON Response<br/>HTTP/8080
    Proxy-->>Route: HTTPS/8443
    Route-->>User: HTTPS/443<br/>Metrics Displayed

    Note over User,ModelReg: Flow 4: Model Registry Operations

    User->>Route: 1. GET /api/modelRegistries/*<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>OAuth Bearer Token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward<br/>HTTPS/8443
    Proxy->>Backend: 2. GET /api/modelRegistries/*<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>User/Group Headers
    Backend->>K8sAPI: 3. Get ModelRegistry CR<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: CR Details
    Backend->>ModelReg: 4. HTTP API Call<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8080<br/>Bearer Token
    ModelReg-->>Backend: Model Metadata
    Backend-->>Proxy: 5. JSON Response<br/>HTTP/8080
    Proxy-->>Route: HTTPS/8443
    Route-->>User: HTTPS/443<br/>Registry Data
